window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When a young man is found hanging inside the Ashford family tomb, Redmond and Haze assume the man had run afoul of the noble family and paid for it with his life. Once they identify the remains, they discover not only the victim’s shocking secrets but that the young man had an unexpected connection to Jason.</p> <p>With few leads and no obvious motive for the murder, will Redmond and Haze solve the case before the killer claims another life?</p>"; 
